Guest access

Bathroom and toilet

Jog and run in Rembrandtpark and Vondelpark with Amsterdam locals. Rent a bicycle to see the city of Amsterdam like locals do.

name: Authentic apartment next to Vondelpark
description:
Our house was built in the 1920's and since then a lot has changed, but you can still feel the character. We've renovated it just the way we like, with modern additions, lots of small details and an overall eye towards history. We are situated right next to the Vondelpark, the Central Park of Amsterdam and we are close to all the bars, shops and restaurants we love. We hope you like it!

The space
You have your own room!

Guest access
When you enter, first you'll climb our staircase, it's big and steep, but on the second floor you'll find our unique space: a small hallway, a big living room and kitchen, your own private room of course and a shared bathroom and toilet. In the bathroom there is a big and comfy bath as well as a large and modern shower.
